{"tid":1926572,"cid":5,"subCid":10,"title":"西班牙封城及法國實施最高防疫 意大利再多3千病例","createTime":"2020-03-15T08:10:50.000Z","updateTime":"2020-03-15T08:10:50.000Z","uid":316569,"like":0,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":1,"replies":[{"pid":"40b8ea6505e24a634ef6b494cc8736960eba53e4","tid":1926572,"uid":316569,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-03-15T08:10:50.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://s.yimg.com/ny/api/res/1.2/34YWocvPoSKsa8t0lUa7Gg--~A/YXBwaWQ9aGlnaGxhbmRlcjtzbT0xO3c9ODAw/https://media-mbst-pub-ue1.s3.amazonaws.com/creatr-uploaded-images/2020-03/c5794900-6648-11ea-bf6a-93fa2772c7bf\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fs.yimg.com%2Fny%2Fapi%2Fres%2F1.2%2F34YWocvPoSKsa8t0lUa7Gg--~A%2FYXBwaWQ9aGlnaGxhbmRlcjtzbT0xO3c9ODAw%2Fhttps%3A%2F%2Fmedia-mbst-pub-ue1.s3.amazonaws.com%2Fcreatr-uploaded-images%2F2020-03%2Fc5794900-6648-11ea-bf6a-93fa2772c7bf&h=246bd512&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<span style=\"font-size: small;\">西班牙封城及法國實施最高防疫 意大利再多3千病例</span><br />\n<br />\n西班牙首相桑切斯宣布，在全國範圍內即時實施「封城」，4600萬人活動受限制。<br />\n西班牙新型肺炎過去24小時內，新增1500宗，累計接近6千宗，不排除未來幾天增至過萬。<br />\n另外，法國總理菲利普亦下令關閉所有非必需公共設施，防疫進入最高階段。<br />\n意大利疫情未有受控跡象，新增個案較對上一天多約兩成，有3497宗，累計超過2萬1千宗，累計1441人死。"}]}